TITLE: Generating Unified Diff Format in Java
DESCRIPTION: Method to generate text in unified diff format from a Patch object, including file names and context lines around changes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/assertj/assertj/blob/main/assertj-core/src/test/resources/diffs/revised.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_6

